This programms doing daemon-backup directory. Daemon.c cannot stop. It works all time, while you kill process(kill pid).
IN log save current changes.
_____________________________________
RUN
gcc backup_daemon.c -o backup
gcc daemon.c -o daemon
./backup path_to_direc path_to_backup
./daemon path_to_direc path_to_backup
_____________________________________
STOP - kill pid(daemon.c) or reboot you OC
check change in log.txt
